01:13:32.500 --> 01:13:33.502
<v 2FF980F9-DA3C-4AC9-9EB3-E53E62EA5FBB>Liam: Mm-hmm.

1381
01:13:38.500 --> 01:13:40.840
<v A2744987-B695-4A4C-99E1-51647E98158F>Kevin: So, um, I like that.

