<v A2744987-B695-4A4C-99E1-51647E98158F>Kevin: I don't think I've seen that in any other game, but you're literally crafting every single tile or what you're going to put on every single tile.

1411
01:14:57.380 --> 01:15:00.199
<v A2744987-B695-4A4C-99E1-51647E98158F>Kevin: So it's all intentional and thoughtful.

1412
