1414
01:15:00.779 --> 01:15:02.460
<v 2FF980F9-DA3C-4AC9-9EB3-E53E62EA5FBB>Liam: You're right.

1415
01:15:02.460 --> 01:15:07.619
<v 2FF980F9-DA3C-4AC9-9EB3-E53E62EA5FBB>Liam: In most farming games, you just take the tiller and you do that on the grass and it turns into dirt, right?

